<section class="py-5 mt-5">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="alert alert-warning" role="alert">
      <strong>Content being developed</strong> — This page presents the Concept of Operations overview. Full detailed content is coming as the project matures.
    </div>

    <h1>Concept of Operations</h1>
    <p class="lead">Terrestrial analogue architecture for cislunar DTN communications.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-4">The Concept</h2>
    <p>{{content.concept}}</p>

    <h2 class="mt-4">RF Link Types</h2>
    <p>The project uses a variety of amateur and experimental RF links as practical analogues for cislunar communication constraints:</p>
    <ul class="list-group list-group-flush mb-4">
      {{#each content.rfLinkTypes}}
      <li class="list-group-item">{{this}}</li>
      {{/each}}
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-4">Why Amateur and Specialist Radio Communities Matter</h2>
    <p>These communities bring essential capabilities to the project:</p>
    <div class="row g-3 mt-2">
      {{#each content.whyCommunityMatters}}
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="card h-100">
          <div class="card-body">
            <p class="mb-0">{{this}}</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      {{/each}}
    </div>

    <h2 class="mt-5">Expected Outcomes</h2>
    <ul class="list-group list-group-flush mb-4">
      {{#each content.expectedOutcomes}}
      <li class="list-group-item">
        <span class="badge bg-success me-2">✓</span>{{this}}
      </li>
      {{/each}}
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-4">NASA References</h2>
    <p>Key NASA resources on Delay-Tolerant Networking and cislunar communications:</p>
    <div class="list-group mb-4">
      {{#each content.nasaReferences}}
      <a href="{{url}}" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <h3 class="h6 mb-1">{{title}}</h3>
        <p class="mb-0 small text-muted">{{description}}</p>
      </a>
      {{/each}}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
